[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man charged over gas explosion at Newport house

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been charged over an explosion at a house in Newport.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gwent Police said a 50-year-old had been charged with arson with intent to endanger life following the blast on 2 April.
The explosion caused extensive damage to the house and adjoining buildings.
The man is due to stand trial at Cardiff Crown Court on 28 November.
